725861f-a.title: Queens: 138th Street - 90th Avenue
725861f-a.text:
138th Street (McCauley Ave.), east side, south of Jamaica
Ave. The house seen at the left foreground,(about 175 feet south of
Jamaica Ave.) is the Daumer house. C. Carll and J. McAnley were the
owners in 1860 and 1873 respectively.
April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
